  which lay wrapt vp in the roots of Faith.
               The third, (which is Saint Austens) As the Sunne doth
  alwayes communicate his heat and influences (but they are more temperate and
  fruitfull in the Spring) so the Sonne of Righteousnesse, though hee euermore
