                  And the Ship was in the midst of the Sea. It seemeth
  somewhat strange, that our Sauiour Christ, inforcing his Disciples to enter
  into the Sea, and they hauing punctually obey'd his command, that hee should
  punish them with such a dangerous and fearefull tempest. That Gods justice
