  congregation of the Faithfull. And a learned man saith, That the Temples &amp;
  Houses of God did put a new heart and new affections into mens brests. What
  then shall become of those who refuse these publique places of praying and
  praysing of God, and make it a Den of Theeues, working all impietie and
  wickednesse in these sacred Assemblies?
