 dumbe to our requests. judge this silence of our Sruiour to bee verie
  strange, in regard ofthe strangenesse of the circumstances. First of all,
  Because that Fountaine (saith Origen) which was alwaies woont to
  inuite and call vs to drinke, doth now denie water to the Thirstie; the
