                  and
  contentions amongst you? is it not onely from your owne lusts, that fight in
  your members? But Sathan that sower of discord, doth also sollicite and
  incite thereunto euen the holiest and best sort of people. Ecce Satanas
  expeti
                        •
                     it vos, vt cribraret sicut
  triticum, Lo Satan seekes to sift ye, as one would sift and winnow Wheat.
