  incarnate his Sonne, there were some Exorcists amongst the Iewes, which in Gods
  name, and by his vertue and power did cast out Deuils. And in the 19 of the
  Acts it is said, That there were certaine sons of Scena a Iew
  (the Priest) which did this. And Iosephus makes mention of one
  Eleazar, who before Vespasian and his whole Army did cast out
  many Deuils. And of Salomon it is said, That he left some exorcismes
