  like: and being one day busie in preaching, (which was Heauens businesse) they
  told him, That his mother and his brethren were without at the doore, expecting
  that he should come forth vnto them. But he stretching out his hand to his
  Disciples, said, Quae mater? Et qui fratres mei? Who is my mother, and who
  my bretheren? My mother and my brethren are they who doe the will of my
