               In humane Stories we read, that Hannibal was banished
  from Carthage after he had triumphed ouer so many Romane Emperours.
  Lycurgus, was pelted out of Lacedemonia with stones, the Oracles
  hauing as it were celebrated him for a god. Solon, was thrust out of
  Athens after he had giuen them such wholsome Lawes. Themistocles,
